            <lg xml:id="TK873">
<l>ēmuṟ ṟavariṉu mēḻai tamiyaṉāyp </l>
<l>pallār pakaikoḷ pavaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who being alone, incurs the hatred of many is more infatuated than even mad men.</l>
